				\begin{document}$$\sqrt{Dt}$$\end{document} = 7.6(2) Å were found in the As-deposited and Annealed states. As anticipated, the 120 keV Ne+ irradiation resulted in a significant interlayer mixing leading to Dt\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
